version: 0.9.5.137
title: Character Acquisition Engine Phase I
commit: feat(character): add acquisition consensus evidence engine
tag: v0.9.5.137
base: v0.9.5.136
notes:
  - Adds Character Acquisition Engine Phase I as an evidence-only layer.
  - Builds character_acquisition_report.json/xlsx from Character ReOCR observations.
  - Computes observation confidence, vote consensus, crop quality and per-position consensus.
  - Adds character acquisition heatmap for recurring weak character positions.
  - Attaches acquisition counts and confidence to validation detail rows.
  - Does not modify Operational Truth, snapshots, exports, Ground Truth or verified display fields.
